Numerous upgrades and updates include New flooring,  new bedrooms with new closets, a completely renovated kitchen with new appliances,  New Bathrooms, a New Deck, with a new Patio, a New Laundry room, a New  HVAC install, New ducts, a New water heater, new cabinetry & storage, renovated garage,  a large fenced rear yard w/deck, patio & storage shed.
